        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 59–66. Ancylosis spp., male genitalia and sternum VIII. 59–62. A. delicatella. 59. Russia, Sarepta (gen. slide 51/19, O. Bidzilya). 60. HT of ciliella, Iran, Keredj, ♂ (gen. slide GU 3614A; B.M. prep. 2870, NHRS-TOBI000004586; Photographed by Tobias Malm, © 2019 Naturhistoriska riksmuseet; original photo cropped; composed from two photographs). 61. NE Iran, (gen. slide 356/19, O. Bidzilya). 62. Afghanistan, Gulbahar (gen. slide 90/19, O. Bidzilya). 63, 64. A. larissae. 63. Afghanistan, 10 km NW Kabul (gen. slide 331/19, O. Bidzilya). 64. China, Ningxia (gen. slide 370/19, O. Bidzilya). 65. A. rhodochrella, Turkey, Gürün (gen. slide 333/19, O. Bidzilya). 66. A. hellenica, Turkey (gen. slide 130.19, V. Yepishin)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4458029/files/figure.png" .

